resources.string: A.1 Food Runners is a mobile application with a sole objective of empowering small businesses, local food outlets and other businesses with a tool that enables them to reach customers with a few taps on the screen.

A.2 No, for now it is just a prototype of a food delivering app(i.e.,just a food ordering app). In near future, we would like to tie up with a restaurant, cafe or a local food outlet to convert it into an actual food ordering app.
A.3 For the convenience of its users, Food Runners has Cash On Delivery as the only payment option.
A.4 Sorry for the issues. Please mail your issues at the mail ID given below
